Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgCg/Cg1001_7.jpg'}
{2: '???', 3: 'Ooooh, yeah. Public transport is the shizz. Hooyah!'}
{2: '???', 3: "Hi hi, aren't you going to at least give a reply to your former co-worker?"}
{2: '???', 3: "Sigh, if this goes on, I may accidentally let you and Karenina's little secret slip out."}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: '...Can you let me think in peace, Noctis?'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory131.png'}
{2: 'Noctis', 3: "That attitude was why I jumped ship to Cerberus. Can't you treat me the way the Gray Raven Commandant does?"}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: "I can't be sensible with someone who keeps disturbing me through comms.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Noctis', 3: "I'm bored! We're both working with you, so why are we getting such different treatments?"}
{2: 'Noctis', 3: 'But, speaking of which—do you know that the Gray Raven Commandant is a Chief of F.O.S.?'}
{2: 'Noctis', 3: 'But now that commandant is leading a team of... trash.'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "That's your perspective. Can I hang up now?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Noctis', 3: "Fine, I'll pass you the message from HQ if you're in such a hurry."}
{2: 'Noctis', 3: '(Pretentiously) Bianca, your frame is capable of increasing its power output through the overclock unit of your Inver-Device after the modification.'}
{2: 'Noctis', 3: 'Oh, whoa—gotta figure out how to get a set of those from Kurono.'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Is this trade going to turn into a fight?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Noctis', 3: "You'll have to ask the one who sent the message."}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I'll wait for the train on the platform, then.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Noctis', 3: "Aren't you using the motorbike I prepared for you? It's really cool..."}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "This is Bianca. The signal is quite poor here, so I'm terminating the call for now.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'So many Corrupted are gathered here. I should clear them out first.', 4: '1'}
